Method.ХранилищеСистемныхНастроекЗагрузить.Description=Zagruzhaet Result From Storage Settings Manager, As Method Platform Import,\nobekta StandartnoeKhranilishcheNastroekMenedzher, no C podderzhkoy dliny Key Manager\nbolee 128 Symbols putem kheshirovaniya Parts, kotoraya prevyshaet 96 Symbols.\nKrome togo, vozvrashchaet ukazannoe Value By Default, If Settings Dont naydeny.\nEsli Objects Tools SokhranenieDannykhPolzovatelya, vozvrashchaetsya Value By Default Debug Flag.\nV vozvrashchaemom znachenii ochishchayutsya References To nesushchestvuyushchiy Object In Base Schema, A imenno\:\n- vozvrashchaemaya Ref zamenyaetsya To ukazannoe Value By Default;\n- From Schema Type Array References udalyayutsya;\n- U Schema Type Structure T Type Key Dont menyaetsya, A Value ustanavlivaetsya Neopredeleno;\n- analiz Table In Schema Type Array, Structure, Type vypolnyaetsya Recursively.
